https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null Madhava Menon (Nedumudi Venu) is a well respected retired police officer who has two daughters, Narasimhan. IPS (Sarath Kumar), an efficient police officer in Tamil Nadu, married Meera and Nandagopan (Jagadish), an officer in Kerala Police who married Meena. They all live very happily. The state legislative election is announced in the state. There happens a twist in Madhava Menon's life. Achante Aanmakkal
